item.title: Beko
item.description: Beko /bɛkoʊ/ (sometimes stylized as beko) is a Turkish domestic appliance and consumer electronics brand of Arçelik A.Ş. controlled by Koç Holding. Source Source

item.title: Turkish Airlines
item.description: Turkish Airlines (Turkish: Türk Hava Yolları) is the national flag carrier airline of Turkey. As of 2018, it operates scheduled services to 304 destinations in Europe, Asia, Africa, and the Americas, making it the largest carrier in the world by number of passenger destinations (excluding regional brands). It serves more destinations non-stop from a single airport than any other airline in the world. Source Source
